data.description: Welcome Home to this charming Mid-Century brick ranch nestled in the well-established neighborhood of Merrimac Point! This 3-Bed, 1.5-Bath beauty has been meticulously maintained and updated, offering the perfect blend of comfort and Mid-Century style. Right inside, discover an updated kitchen boasting custom cabinets and granite countertops. Fresh paint and refinished hardwood floors throughout add to the home's inviting ambiance, while an encapsulated crawlspace & vinyl wrapped trim ensures peace of mind for years to come. With both an attached garage and a detached garage/workshop equipped with electricity, there's ample space for parking and projects. Enjoy lazy afternoons in the sunroom, entertain guests on the deck, or let furry friends roam free in the large fenced backyard. This home is 100% move-in ready, just waiting for you to make it your own!
